title: 50 Happiest Songs Ever! + Eddie's Toilet Paper Experiment + Amy Gets DM From Meteorologist
itunes:title: 50 Happiest Songs Ever! + Eddie's Toilet Paper Experiment + Amy Gets DM From Meteorologist
description:
Amy got a message from a local meteorologist who was concerned about Amy's son after hearing about his fear of severe weather. He too had similar fears as a kid and reached out to her to see about helping him out. Bobby shares the top five songs from a "50 Happiest Songs" list and also shares his own personal top five list! Plus, Bobby sends Eddie into the bathroom to see if he can tell the difference between different toilet paper brands!
